	        'No somos responsables por incumplimientos atribuibles a terceros, circunstancias imprevisibles o fuerza mayor (clima, decisiones gubernamentales, huelgas, etc.).' => 'We are not responsible for breaches attributable to third parties, unforeseeable circumstances or force majeure, such as weather, government decisions or strikes.',
